{{Top|leg}}
'''Patrol Plaza''' was a square on the planet [[Taris/Legends|Taris]]. In [[3964 BBY]], [[Taris Holofeed]] interviewed [[Sector Constable|Constable]] [[Noana Sowrs|Sowrs]] of the [[Taris Civil Authority]] about the role of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in law enforcement on Taris at Patrol Plaza.<ref name="TTHPE">{{KOTORbackups|0}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Patrol Plaza first mentioned in the "[[The Taris Holofeed: Prime Edition]]," an in-universe issue of the [[Taris Holofeed]] written by [[John Jackson Miller]] that introduced the first arc of the [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic (comic series)|''Knights of the Old Republic'' comic series]].<ref name="TTHPE" /> The mention of Patrol Plaza in the article had made some fans consider that the square was the location of the [[Jedi Tower]] but this over-interpretation had been denied by John Jackson Miller.<ref name="JJMcd#9">{{Faraway|subdomain=blog|url=2010/02/kotor-coundown-9-just-asked-questions.html|text=KOTOR Countdown #9: Just-Asked Questions, Part One}}</ref>

